ProtoDefines:
. "A sequence $\{u_n\}$ in a metric space $(A,\rho)$ \term{ 
   converges } to $u\in A$ if \begin{equation} 
   \lim_{n\to\infty}\rho(u_n,u)=0. \end{equation} In this case 
   we say that $\lim_{n\to\infty}u_n=u$."
